Package: base.plus
Title: Additions to Base R
Description:
    This package provides a library of R functions, operators, and
    utilities that extend base R with "quality of life" improvements. This
    package has no external dependencies, as it is ony designed to extend
    functions included with the base R distribution.
Version: 0.1.0
